SURF GREATRIVER PG
==================
**IF YOU WANT TO EDIT THIS MAP PLEASE INBOX ME**
### **Description**
This is one of my finest maps I've made so far
i made this map pretty much from scratch but using the measurements from the map surf greatriver knk

This map was firstly made for my group to have fun around but I've decided i want to release it

Later i might add a few small details and areas but for now this is just how it is nice and simple

**Areas effecting in the recreate**
- No splash back board behind the portals to jail and top
- New redesign of top and jail
- New areas where the shotgun platform
- Smoother ramps (more speed :D)
- New weapons around the map
- 2 secret awps
- map spawn ratio is 20:20 ct and t

Thanks for downloading! 
(folder size and contents 5.6mb - readME/bsp/nav
